---
---

<footer class="footer">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="footer-top">
			<div class="footer-brand">
				<a href="/" class="logo">
					<span class="logo-text">Mibeko</span>
					<span class="logo-dot">.</span>
				</a>
				<p class="brand-desc text-gray">
					La première plateforme d'intelligence juridique en République du Congo. Accédez à vos droits, partout, tout le temps.
				</p>
				<div class="socials">
					<a href="#" class="social-link" aria-label="LinkedIn">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"></path><rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"></rect><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"></circle></svg>
					</a>
					<a href="#" class="social-link" aria-label="Twitter">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 4s-.7 2.1-2 3.4c1.6 10-9.4 17.3-18 11.6 2.2.1 4.4-.6 6-2C3 15.5.5 9.6 3 5c2.2 2.6 5.6 4.1 9 4-.9-4.2 4-6.6 7-3.8 1.1 0 3-1.2 3-1.2z"></path></svg>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="footer-links">
				<div class="link-group">
					<h4 class="group-title text-white">Produit</h4>
					<ul>
						<li><a href="#features">Fonctionnalités</a></li>
						<li><a href="#audience">Pour qui ?</a></li>
						<li><a href="#download">Télécharger l'App</a></li>
						<li><a href="https://app.mibeko.fr">Portail Pro</a></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="link-group">
					<h4 class="group-title text-white">Légal</h4>
					<ul>
						<li><a href="#">Mentions Légales</a></li>
						<li><a href="#">Politique de Confidentialité</a></li>
						<li><a href="#">CGU</a></li>
						<li><a href="mailto:mibeko@benaja-bendo.fr">Contact</a></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="footer-newsletter">
				<h4 class="group-title text-white">Restez informé</h4>
				<p class="text-gray" style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
					Inscrivez-vous pour recevoir les dernières actualités juridiques et les mises à jour de la plateforme.
				</p>
				<form class="newsletter-form">
					<input type="email" placeholder="Votre adresse email" required class="newsletter-input" />
					<button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary newsletter-btn">S'inscrire</button>
				</form>
				<p class="rgpd-text">
					En vous inscrivant, vous acceptez notre politique de confidentialité. Conformité RGPD assurée.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="footer-bottom text-gray">
			<p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Mibeko. Tous droits réservés.</p>
			<p>Fait avec passion pour le droit congolais.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	.footer {
		background-color: var(--color-navy-light);
		padding: 6rem 0 2rem;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
	}

	.footer-top {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 2fr 3fr 2fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.logo {
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		color: var(--color-white);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.logo-dot {
		color: var(--color-gold);
	}

	.brand-desc {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		max-width: 300px;
	}

	.socials {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.social-link {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 40px;
		height: 40px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background-color: var(--color-navy-lighter);
		color: var(--color-white);
		transition: all 0.3s;
	}

	.social-link:hover {
		background-color: var(--color-gold);
		color: var(--color-navy);
		transform: translateY(-3px);
	}

	.footer-links {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-around;
	}

	.group-title {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.link-group ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.8rem;
	}

	.link-group a {
		color: var(--color-gray);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		transition: color 0.3s;
	}

	.link-group a:hover {
		color: var(--color-gold);
	}

	.newsletter-form {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.8rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
	}

	.newsletter-input {
		padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
		background-color: var(--color-navy-lighter);
		color: var(--color-white);
		font-family: var(--font-main);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		outline: none;
		transition: border-color 0.3s;
	}

	.newsletter-input:focus {
		border-color: var(--color-gold);
	}

	.newsletter-input::placeholder {
		color: var(--color-gray);
	}

	.newsletter-btn {
		width: 100%;
		padding: 0.8rem;
	}

	.rgpd-text {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--color-gray);
		opacity: 0.7;
	}

	.footer-bottom {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		padding-top: 2rem;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 992px) {
		.footer-top {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 3rem;
		}

		.footer-links {
			justify-content: flex-start;
			gap: 4rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.footer-bottom {
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 1rem;
			text-align: center;
		}
	}
</style>
